@treemaker/origami-simulator includes a modern TypeScript port of the dynamic
solver from Origami Simulator.

Origami Simulator:
  Copyright (c) 2018 Amanda Ghassaei
  Repository: https://github.com/amandaghassaei/OrigamiSimulator
  Source commit used for this port: 7855983a613c879c171b2b1557f8cd102d2640cf
  Upstream license: MIT

Primary upstream source files:
  js/dynamic/dynamicSolver.js
  js/model.js
  js/beam.js
  js/crease.js
  js/node.js
  index.html shader blocks:
    normalCalc
    thetaCalcShader
    updateCreaseGeo
    velocityCalcShader
    positionCalcShader
    positionCalcVerletShader
    velocityCalcVerletShader

The TreeMaker package removes the original UI/global DOM layer and keeps the
solver as a FOLD-in, frame-out library API.
